snippet.title: [Satellaview] Kirby no Omochabako: Ball Rally
snippet.description:
http://superfamicom.org/blog

Recorded some footage of Ball Rally, extended from the bssurekure video, to show some extended gameplay.

Thanks for watching! As with all YouTube channels, likes, subscriptions and comments are welcome - but I presume that is to be expected, yes?

If you want to show your support in other ways, feel free to use StreamLabs!
https://streamlabs.com/kiddocabbusses/tip
